        <updateDate>2017-07-08T15:39:12Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Dreamer Protection Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits the obligation or expenditure of federal funds to apprehend, detain, or remove from the United States any alien who was granted deferred action under the Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals Program announced on June 15, 2012, if the alien lost their deferred action status solely as a result of action taken by the President or any other federal official with respect to such program.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Dreamer Protection Act</title>
    <titles>
